  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Treatment resistant schizophrenic or schizoaffective disorder under therapy with
             clozapine,

          -  Age between 18 and 70,

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  No informed consent,

          -  Intolerance with respect to ziprasidone or risperidone,

          -  Contraindications with respect to these substances,

          -  Gravidity or missing anticonceptive safety

          -  Substance dependance (excluded nicotin)
      </textblock>
